<LanguageData>

  <!-- EN: large fire -->
  <VFET_LargeFire.label>大きな焚き火</VFET_LargeFire.label>
  <!-- EN: Produces large amounts of heat and smoke, and burns out after a quadrum. The light from a
  large fire is visible from afar. As long as it’s burning outdoors, there is a higher chance of
  wild men wandering in, as well as raids. As with all heat sources, it must be placed indoors so it
  has a closed space to heat. Refuelable. Due to the size and instability of it, it may eject sparks
  around itself that may start a fire. -->
  <VFET_LargeFire.description>大量の熱と煙を発生させ、15日で燃え尽きます。屋外で燃えている場合、遠くからも光が見えます。屋外で燃えている限り、野生人が迷い込んだり、襲撃が発生しやすくなります。すべての熱源と同様、屋内に設置して閉じた空間を暖める必要があります。燃料補給可能。大きく不安定なため、周囲に火花を飛ばして火災を起こすことがあります。</VFET_LargeFire.description>

</LanguageData>
